data.description: Stunning 2 Bed, 2 Bath Condo with Rooftop Terrace. Experience the pinnacle of contemporary urban living in this meticulously designed 2-bedroom, 2-bath condo. A recent kitchen remodel showcases stainless steel elegance alongside hardwood floors, creating an ambiance of modern luxury. Quartz countertops in the kitchen add a touch of sophistication and durability. The heart of the living space is adorned with a captivating two-story window, infusing the area with abundant natural light and offering a striking focal point. A captivating spiral staircase leads to a loft-style bedroom. with an ensuite bath, offering a private retreat. Step onto your private rooftop terrace - an oasis for entertainment against the backdrop of the vibrant city. With the added convenience of two assigned parking spaces, you'll always find a place to call home for your vehicles. Nestled near the Beltline, Krog Street Market, Little Five Points, Candler Park, Inman Park and many of Atlanta's hottest new shopping and dining spots. This centrally located condo is less than 30 minutes to Atlanta's Hartsfield Jackson International Airport and only 2 blocks away from a MARTA station for a fast commute to the airport. The move-in ready condo invites you to embrace urban life at its finest in style.
